      <div class="nav-dropdown"><a href="Icons.html">Resources <svg class="nav-chevron" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></a><div class="nav-dropdown-menu"><a href="Icons.html"><svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z"/></svg>Icons</a><a href="Logos.html"><svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09z"/></svg>Product Logo</a><a href="Illustrations.html"><svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5A2.25 2.25 0 0022.5 18.75V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0020.25 3H3.75A2.25 2.25 0 001.5 5.25v13.5A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 21z"/></svg>Illustrations</a></div></div>
      <div id="div" style="width: 16px;"></div>
      <button id="themeToggle" class="icon-btn" title="Toggle Theme">
        <svg id="moonIcon" width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="display:none;"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1111.21 3 7 7 0 0021 12.79z"/></svg>
        <svg id="sunIcon" width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="display:block;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"/><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"/><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"/><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"/><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div id="components-layout" class="components-layout">
    <main class="main-panel">
      <div id="page-header-area" class="page-header-area">
        <h1 class="page-title">Zia Experience</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">Design guidelines for integrating Zia AI experiences into Endpoint Central to help IT admins understand, prioritize, and act on endpoint insights faster.</p>
      </div>

      <div id="main-content-area" class="main-content-area">
        <div id="main-content-inner" class="main-content-inner">

          <!-- Overview 1 -->
                      <h2 id="overview-intro">Zia Logo</h2>
            <p>Zia brings intelligence directly into endpoint workflows, helping IT teams quickly understand device health, prioritize risks, and take the right action with confidence.</p>
          <div id="div-2" class="theme-container" style="border-radius:16px;padding:34px;border:1px solid var(--prism-border);box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:40px;">
            <img src="assets/zia-logo.png" alt="Zia Logo" style="width:30px;display:block;">
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider">

          <!-- Overview 2 -->
                      <h2 id="overview">Zia Input Field</h2>
            <p>Ask Zia anything about your endpoint environment—from device health and patch failures to compliance drift, vulnerabilities, and remediation steps.</p>
          <div id="div-3" class="theme-container" style="border-radius:16px;padding:24px;border:1px solid var(--prism-border);box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:40px;">
            <div class="zia-input-wrap">
              <input type="text" class="zia-input" placeholder="Ask Zia anything..." />
              <div class="zia-input-row">
                <div class="zia-input-icons">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.42881" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13.5312 5L7.57602 16.108"/></svg>
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.44 11.05l-9.19 9.19a6 6 0 01-8.49-8.49l9.19-9.19a4 4 0 015.66 5.66l-9.2 9.19a2 2 0 01-2.83-2.83l8.49-8.48"/></svg>
                </div>
                <button class="zia-send-btn">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 2L11 13"/><path d="M22 2L15 22L11 13L2 9L22 2Z"/></svg>
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider">

          <!-- Ask Zia -->
          <h2 id="ask-zia">Ask Zia</h2>
          <p>A full conversational interface where users can ask questions, receive intelligent answers, and take guided actions on their endpoint environment.</p>
          <div id="div-5" class="theme-container" style="border-radius:16px;padding:24px;border:1px solid var(--prism-border);box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:40px;">
            <div class="zia-chat">
              <div class="zia-chat-bar">
                <span class="zia-chat-dot"></span>
                <span class="zia-chat-dot"></span>
                <span class="zia-chat-dot"></span>
                <span class="zia-chat-title">Zia Assistant</span>
              </div>
              <div class="zia-chat-body" style="max-width:100%;margin:0 auto;gap:22px;border:none;padding:40px 40px 20px 40px;">
                <div class="zia-chat-hero">
                  <img src="assets/zia-logo.png" alt="Zia">
                  <h3>How can we assist you?</h3>
                  <p>Choose a prompt below or write your own to start chatting with Zia</p>
                </div>
                <div class="zia-prompt-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);">
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg> Patch Management</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">Analyzes historical patch data, CVE trends, and exploit databases &amp; more.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg> Remote Troubleshooting</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">Runs diagnostics and either resolves it, escalates with logs &amp; more.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg> Security &amp; Compliance</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">Scans endpoint behavior, logs, network activity &amp; more</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card default">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/></svg> Configuration</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">Analyzes device usage, security gaps, Suggests optimal config policies.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 3h-8l-2 4h12l-2-4z"/></svg> Asset Management</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">Predicts when hardware will fail, tracks actual usage &amp; more.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg> Others</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">BitLocker management, browser security controls &amp; more.</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="zia-input-wrap" style="max-width:100%;">
                  <input type="text" class="zia-input" placeholder="Ask Zia assist" />
                  <div class="zia-input-row">
                    <div class="zia-input-icons">
                      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.42881" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13.5312 5L7.57602 16.108"/></svg>
                      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.44 11.05l-9.19 9.19a6 6 0 01-8.49-8.49l9.19-9.19a4 4 0 015.66 5.66l-9.2 9.19a2 2 0 01-2.83-2.83l8.49-8.48"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <button class="zia-send-btn">
                      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 2L11 13"/><path d="M22 2L15 22L11 13L2 9L22 2Z"/></svg>
                    </button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider">

          <!-- Zia Button -->
          <h2 id="zia-button">Zia Button</h2>
          <p>A quick-access button that lets users invoke Zia from anywhere in the interface with a single click.</p>
          <div id="div-4" class="theme-container" style="border-radius:16px;padding:24px;border:1px solid var(--prism-border);box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:40px;">
            <button class="zia-text-btn">
              <svg class="zia-sparkle-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 15.28 15.28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <defs>
                  <linearGradient id="zia-spark1" x1="0" y1="5" x2="13" y2="5.8" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><stop stop-color="#1D69D4"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#B71BD9"/></linearGradient>
                  <linearGradient id="zia-spark2" x1="9.3" y1="1.3" x2="15.9" y2="1.7" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><stop stop-color="#1D69D4"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#B71BD9"/></linearGradient>
                </defs>
                <path class="zia-spark-path1" d="M6.247 3.717l.47 1.307a3.56 3.56 0 0 0 2.114 2.114l1.306.47c.118.043.118.21 0 .252l-1.306.47a3.56 3.56 0 0 0-2.114 2.115l-.47 1.306c-.043.118-.21.118-.252 0l-.47-1.306a3.56 3.56 0 0 0-2.115-2.114l-1.306-.471c-.118-.043-.118-.21 0-.252l1.306-.47A3.56 3.56 0 0 0 5.525 5.024l.47-1.307c.043-.118.21-.118.252 0Z" fill="url(#zia-spark1)"/>
                <path class="zia-spark-path2" d="M12.126.578l.238.661a2.01 2.01 0 0 0 1.177 1.177l.662.238c.06.022.06.106 0 .128l-.662.238a2.01 2.01 0 0 0-1.177 1.177l-.238.661c-.022.06-.106.06-.128 0l-.238-.661a2.01 2.01 0 0 0-1.177-1.177l-.662-.238c-.06-.022-.06-.106 0-.128l.662-.238A2.01 2.01 0 0 0 11.76 1.24l.238-.661c.022-.06.107-.06.128 0Z" fill="url(#zia-spark2)"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="zia-btn-label">Zia Workflow</span>
            </button>
            <div style="width:16px;"></div>
            <button class="zia-text-btn">
              <svg class="zia-sparkle-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 15.28 15.28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <defs>
                  <linearGradient id="zia-spark3" x1="0" y1="5" x2="13" y2="5.8" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><stop stop-color="#1D69D4"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#B71BD9"/></linearGradient>
                  <linearGradient id="zia-spark4" x1="9.3" y1="1.3" x2="15.9" y2="1.7" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><stop stop-color="#1D69D4"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#B71BD9"/></linearGradient>
                </defs>
                <path class="zia-spark-path1" d="M6.247 3.717l.47 1.307a3.56 3.56 0 0 0 2.114 2.114l1.306.47c.118.043.118.21 0 .252l-1.306.47a3.56 3.56 0 0 0-2.114 2.115l-.47 1.306c-.043.118-.21.118-.252 0l-.47-1.306a3.56 3.56 0 0 0-2.115-2.114l-1.306-.471c-.118-.043-.118-.21 0-.252l1.306-.47A3.56 3.56 0 0 0 5.525 5.024l.47-1.307c.043-.118.21-.118.252 0Z" fill="url(#zia-spark3)"/>
                <path class="zia-spark-path2" d="M12.126.578l.238.661a2.01 2.01 0 0 0 1.177 1.177l.662.238c.06.022.06.106 0 .128l-.662.238a2.01 2.01 0 0 0-1.177 1.177l-.238.661c-.022.06-.106.06-.128 0l-.238-.661a2.01 2.01 0 0 0-1.177-1.177l-.662-.238c-.06-.022-.06-.106 0-.128l.662-.238A2.01 2.01 0 0 0 11.76 1.24l.238-.661c.022-.06.107-.06.128 0Z" fill="url(#zia-spark4)"/>
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider">

          <!-- Zia Sidebar -->
          <h2 id="zia-sidebar">Zia Sidebar</h2>
          <p>A persistent side panel that keeps Zia accessible alongside your workflow, displaying conversation history and quick access to previous sessions.</p>
          <div id="div-6" class="theme-container" style="border-radius:16px;padding:24px;border:1px solid var(--prism-border);box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:40px;">
            <div class="zia-chat">
              <div class="zia-chat-bar">
                <span class="zia-chat-dot"></span>
                <span class="zia-chat-dot"></span>
                <span class="zia-chat-dot"></span>
                <span class="zia-chat-title">Zia Assistant</span>
              </div>
              <div class="zia-chat-body">
                <div class="zia-chat-hero">
                  <img src="assets/zia-logo.png" alt="Zia">
                  <h3>How can we assist you?</h3>
                  <p>Choose a prompt below or write your own to start chatting with Zia</p>
                </div>
                <div class="zia-prompt-grid">
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg> Patch Management</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">Analyzes historical patch data, CVE trends, and exploit databases &amp; more.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card default">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/></svg> Configuration</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">Analyzes device usage, security gaps, Suggests optimal config policies.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 3h-8l-2 4h12l-2-4z"/></svg> Asset Management</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">Predicts when hardware will fail, tracks actual usage &amp; more.</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="zia-prompt-card">
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-title"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg> Others</div>
                    <div class="zia-prompt-card-desc">BitLocker management, browser security controls &amp; more.</div>
                  </div>
